Place steak in shallow non-metallic dish. Pour 1/4 cup teriyaki sauce over steak. Cover, marinate 15 minutes in refrigerator. Thread pineapple chunks, steak and bell peppers onto skewers. Brush with remaining marinade. Grill or broil 8 to 12 minutes turning and brushing occasionally with marinade during grilling. Discard any remaining marinade. Serve with rice, if desired.